ナーである祐美子が、銀行の頭取である父を持つ藤宮律子を男達にレイプさせ、それをネタに脅そうというのだ。そこで純は、それよりも先に律子に近づく。\r\n男嫌いの律子ではあったが、純の強引なアプローチについには身体を許してしまう。そして純は、律子を利用し『ハングリーベア』乗っ取りの計画を実行に移すのだった。"}],"crt":[{"id":76600,"image":"","name":"大久保純","desc":"吉野裕行"},{"id":76601,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/37/8d/76601_crt_D6G0v.jpg","name":"神谷美香","desc":"前川優子"},{"id":76602,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e2/49/76602_crt_19M2L.jpg","name":"铃原さやか","desc":"永瀬江美弥"},{"id":76603,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bb/f7/76603_crt_wX5QP.jpg","name":"藤宫律子","desc":"主角"},{"id":97977,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5d/9d/97977_crt_pCpML.jpg","name":"岬祐美子","desc":"配角"}],"staff":[{"id":2662,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/17/10/2662_prsn_2Pr53.jpg","name":"スワラ・プロ","desc":"音效"},{"id":19599,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/41/0e/19599_prsn_vmBb4.jpg","name":"ちぇりーそふと","desc":"原作"},{"id":2224,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/37/34/2224_prsn_Xjp2q.jpg","name":"DISCOVERY","desc":"製作"},{"id":6009,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/95/6e/6009_prsn_Z7JRZ.jpg","name":"渡辺明夫","desc":"原画"},{"id":3047,"image":"","name":"竹内哲也","desc":"原画"},{"id":12672,"image":"","name":"関一彦","desc":"剪辑"},{"id":7606,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/78/40/7606_prsn_pOL7h.jpg","name":"小林直人","desc":"音效"},{"id":24267,"image":"","name":"浦狩裕樹","desc":"音响"},{"id":1727,"image":"","name":"和田秀美","desc":"色彩设计"},{"id":1640,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/22/f5/1640_prsn_jEiJ7.jpg","name":"長森佳容","desc":"原画"},{"id":3339,"image":"","name":"藪野浩二","desc":"原画"},{"id":34372,"image":"","name":"杉本光司","desc":"原画"},{"id":692,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b6/64/692_prsn_uUB8f.jpg","name":"新房昭之","desc":"导演"},{"id":27201,"image":"","name":"齊藤寛","desc":"原画"},{"id":3756,"image":"","name":"宮下雄次","desc":"原画"},{"id":2264,"image":"","name":"安彦守","desc":"原画"},{"id":38133,"image":"","name":"古川信之","desc":"原画"},{"id":12906,"image":"","name":"加藤清司郎","desc":"原画"},{"id":2511,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f5/d1/2511_prsn_N7pgM.jpg","name":"高寺たけし","desc":"音响监督"},{"id":26901,"image":"","name":"